headline.main: CLOSER VICHY TIES, WITH BERLIN DUE; French Negotiator Returns From Paris With Aide of Reich's Ambassador

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Sept. 26 -- Developments In Franco-German relations may be expected in the near future, it is stated. Negotiations have been quiescent virtually since the opening of hostilities against Russia, but now, according to an authorized source here, "the German Government is sufficiently relieved of preoccupations regarding the Eastern Front to be able to devote its attention again to relations with France."
